Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.56,0:00:06.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nostalgia sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.84,0:00:09.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi, bagaimana dia sekarang, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.02,0:00:12.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gawat, gawat, gawat, gawat, gawat...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.78,0:00:13.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sini rupanya!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.03,0:00:15.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian berdua harus tenang!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.96,0:00:19.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hiro telah diculik!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:53.56,0:01:55.10,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Tempat selanjutnya...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.18,0:01:57.68,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Meski agak jauh,\Nke toko baju favoritku, yuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.08,0:02:00.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kali ini akan kupilihkan\Nbaju yang cocok untukmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.58,0:02:03.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.56,0:02:07.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, apa maksudnya ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.90,0:02:11.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau mau culik, culik aku saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.42,0:02:13.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Soal uang tebusan, Papa pasti akan bayar!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.66,0:02:16.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau salah paham, Erika.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.48,0:02:17.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.24,0:02:19.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, tiba-tiba begini.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.38,0:02:21.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih untuk selama ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.48,0:02:24.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu dulu, Hiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.14,0:02:28.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibunya Hiro?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.94,0:02:31.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu namanya bukan penculikan!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.24,0:02:33.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.80,0:02:36.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namanya orang tua, masa menculik?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.38,0:02:39.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka tiba-tiba\Nmemaksa dia masuk mobil, tuh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.42,0:02:42.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu namanya memaksa pulang anak yang kabur.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.64,0:02:45.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kupikir dia ke sini\Natas persetujuan orang tuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.10,0:02:50.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kehilangan seseorang dengan cara seperti ini\Nmembuatku kesepian.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.18,0:02:53.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Andai dia bisa jadi tutorku lebih lama.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.42,0:02:54.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi hilang saingan, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:54.96,0:02:55.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saingan?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.10,0:02:57.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, Hiro itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.14,0:03:01.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia kabur karena tidak ingin\Nmenemui tunangannya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.22,0:03:05.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.80,0:03:07.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semua pemerannya sudah lengkap.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:07.80,0:03:10.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kesempatan membalikkan\Nkeadaan telah datang!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.52,0:03:11.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bicara apa kau ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.84,0:03:15.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maksudmu, waktu pertemuan Hiro\Ndan tunangannya sudah tiba?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.62,0:03:18.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, arti ucapan Hiro itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.86,0:03:20.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Terima kasih untuk selama ini."
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.16,0:03:23.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita sudah tidak bisa bertemu lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.36,0:03:26.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana ini, Nagi?\NAku tidak mau itu terjadi!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.24,0:03:28.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana mungkin kubiarkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.08,0:03:30.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.36,0:03:31.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, Nagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.72,0:03:35.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang sedang kau coba lakukan itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.82,0:03:38.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,akan mengubah takdirnya Hiro!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.86,0:03:40.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau tetap akan pergi?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.32,0:03:45.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak punya alasan untuk tidak!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.90,0:03:53.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah telanjur sampai di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.12,0:03:55.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tenang dulu!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.54,0:03:57.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka pasti mengerti penjelasanku!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.18,0:04:00.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampaikan dengan hormat dan jujur.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.72,0:04:03.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Aku menyukai Segawa!"
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.02,0:04:06.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Mohon pertimbangkan lagi\Nsoal pertunangannya!"
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.34,0:04:09.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau sampai sebegitunya...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.72,0:04:10.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.12,0:04:11.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku suka kau!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.60,0:04:13.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini dia!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.76,0:04:18.08,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Mohon permisi!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.22,0:04:18.90,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Iya?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.88,0:04:21.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku salah tempat...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.84,0:04:22.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permisi!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.70,0:04:23.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.94,0:04:27.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Segawa, ada di mana kau ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.42,0:04:30.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dia tidak di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, Segawa!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.80,0:04:38.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.86,0:04:39.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.86,0:04:44.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo bergegas, Hiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:51.78,0:04:52.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak akan lari dari takdir.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.60,0:04:59.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kuhadapi!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.64,0:05:05.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan buka sendiri jalan takdirku!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.74,0:05:07.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.08,0:05:09.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,cobalah untuk
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,mengubah takdirku.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dapat peringkat dua?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.78,0:05:25.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yang selalu peringkat satu\Ndi 15 tahun hidupku ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.76,0:05:27.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Segawa Hiro...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.40,0:05:29.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Laki-laki seperti apa dia?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.54,0:05:34.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku dari SMP Kakinokizaka,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,namaku Segawa Hiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.82,0:05:38.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Salam kenal.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.08,0:05:43.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia ternyata perempuan!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.72,0:05:46.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak menyangka\Nkita masuk SMA yang sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.32,0:05:49.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pada tes tengah semester pertama,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:49.60,0:05:51.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku lah yang akan jadi peringkat satu!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.30,0:05:56.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya Segawa peringkat satu!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:56.66,0:05:59.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nilai 100 setiap mapel, keren banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.32,0:06:00.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dewa, kah?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.42,0:06:02.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hebat, ya? Aku jadi kagum.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.14,0:06:06.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini pertama kalinya aku sefrustrasi ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.92,0:06:10.98,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Kakak,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.08,0:06:12.30,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,main gim, yuk!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.60,0:06:15.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sibuk persiapan tes akhir semester.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.24,0:06:18.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tes akhir, katamu?\NYang tengah baru saja selesai.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.14,0:06:22.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah masuk SMA,\NKakak belajar melulu, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.40,0:06:24.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa untungnya jadi introver begini?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.50,0:06:26.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berisik kau ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.56,0:06:29.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau sebegitunya tidak mau main,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,tidak bakalan kuajak lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.46,0:06:32.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar, Kakak bodoh!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.06,0:06:34.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakak bodoh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.54,0:06:40.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pada tes berikutnya pasti,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:40.46,0:06:41.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku yang menang!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.38,0:06:46.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa begini?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.68,0:06:48.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia memang beda level.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.64,0:06:52.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kudengar cuma dia yang berhasil\Nmenjawab soal jebakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.16,0:06:56.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan aku gagal dapat nilai 100\Ngara-gara soal jebakan itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.76,0:07:00.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi Segawa itu\Norangnya selalu sendiri, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.16,0:07:04.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini pertama kalinya\Naku bertemu orang yang mirip aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.34,0:07:09.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak, deh. Dia tidak mau\Ndisamakan oleh kakak, lah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.92,0:07:10.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:10.82,0:07:13.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin dia malah tidak anggap kau rival.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.78,0:07:17.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang seperti itu\Ntidak tertarik sama orang lain.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.36,0:07:20.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cuma peduli sama diri sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.68,0:07:23.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, tapi sisi itu justru mirip sama Kakak.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.82,0:07:26.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan menang darinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.72,0:07:30.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akhir-akhir ini, kakak sering\Nheboh sendiri bikin kesal.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.94,0:07:35.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tes setelah liburan inilah waktunya!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.56,0:07:38.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demi hari ini aku belajar enam jam\Ntiap hari selama musim panas.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.26,0:07:41.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demi peningkatan kemampuan akademis!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.03,0:07:44.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan samakan dengan diriku semester lalu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.34,0:07:58.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sisa lusa kemarin, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.86,0:08:00.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan remehkan organ dalamku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.90,0:08:04.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Daging yang kucamil tadi pagi penyebabnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.42,0:08:05.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku meremehkannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.94,0:08:08.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa aku tidak bisa menang lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.82,0:08:13.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal usia dan lingkungan\Ntempat belajar kami itu sama.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.98,0:08:15.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa tak bisa menang?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:17.72,0:08:19.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak boleh! Segawa!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.44,0:08:21.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan kembali ke kelas.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demammu 39 derajat, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.98,0:08:26.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Hari ini pulang cepat saja.\N- Aku tidak apa.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.38,0:08:30.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau tidak ikut tes,\Naku tidak bisa jadi peringkat satu.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.38,0:08:34.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mana mungkin aku bisa menang.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.58,0:08:37.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.52,0:08:39.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tetap ikut tes walaupun sedang demam.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.18,0:08:41.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu membuatku kagum.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.16,0:08:47.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yakin kau berusaha keras\Nwalaupun tidak dilihat orang.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.66,0:08:49.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Kau tahu soal itu?\N- Dia bicara!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.78,0:08:52.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah... Aku ada di UKS\Npada hari tes.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.16,0:08:55.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga ikut tes sambil tahan sakit perut
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.32,0:08:56.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi hasilnya buruk.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan ajak aku bicara lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.22,0:09:03.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.30,0:09:06.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan ajak aku bicara lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya aku harus minta maaf kalau begini.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:18.44,0:09:19.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Minta maaf saja, ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:20.00,0:09:22.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi dia menyuruhku\Nuntuk tidak ajak dia bicara.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:22.60,0:09:23.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kok tiba-tiba berubah, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.86,0:09:25.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Gila, ini!\N- Cakep benar dia, sih!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.18,0:09:26.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.22,0:09:31.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai dari hari ini, Segawa pun berubah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.88,0:09:35.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa di momen inilah,\Naku mulai suka padanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:35.64,0:09:37.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudnya coba?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.74,0:09:50.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.64,0:09:53.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi, aku dipanggil seseorang?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.34,0:09:56.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Sachi!\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.08,0:09:57.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sachi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.54,0:09:59.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sachi?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.84,0:10:01.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Sachi?\N- Pasti hantu, 'kan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.44,0:10:03.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sachi.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.26,0:10:04.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.88,0:10:06.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.10,0:10:11.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Busnya lama, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.72,0:10:12.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.18,0:10:15.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habis ini harus bagaimana, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.66,0:10:18.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pergi sejauh yang kita bisa, mungkin?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.06,0:10:19.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.22,0:10:22.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku terkejut.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.26,0:10:25.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak sangka Umino cuma bawa 1.000 yen.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.50,0:10:27.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bawa sepeser pun, sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.14,0:10:29.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maafkan aku!\NAku tidak sangka bakal begini.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.20,0:10:32.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa-bisanya aku\Ntarik tangan Segawa terus kabur.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.60,0:10:34.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang telah aku lakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.18,0:10:36.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku tidak menyesal!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.72,0:10:40.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,lama-lama lapar juga, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.54,0:10:44.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejak kapan kau pulang?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.78,0:10:46.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sama sekali tidak sadar.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:46.64,0:10:48.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dulu kau pindah ke Tiongkok, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.42,0:10:50.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ke Shenzhen, Provinsi Guangdong.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.74,0:10:52.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat datang kembali, Ai!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.56,0:10:54.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang kau sudah besar, ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.80,0:10:58.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Beneran! Kami sampai pangling!\N- Setuju!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.38,0:10:59.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apalagi soal pakaiannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.74,0:11:02.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini pekerjaanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.30,0:11:03.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pekerjaan apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.54,0:11:04.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rahasia.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.02,0:11:06.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sudah bekerja ternyata?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.06,0:11:10.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai dari dulu sudah\Nseperti orang dewasa, sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.06,0:11:12.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf sudah buat menunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.66,0:11:13.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katsudon kesukaanmu!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.92,0:11:18.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dulu kau sering mampir untuk makan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.14,0:11:19.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai bawa uang saku segala.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.48,0:11:22.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pelanggan setia.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana ayah dan ibumu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.90,0:11:26.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau soal itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:27.98,0:11:30.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keluarga kami berpisah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:30.64,0:11:31.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.90,0:11:32.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.04,0:11:36.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami bersama selama\Ntujuh tahun di Tiongkok.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.68,0:11:37.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayah ke Singapura.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:38.18,0:11:39.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu ke Prancis.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.58,0:11:42.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sementara Ai memilih untuk hidup di Jepang.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.94,0:11:46.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oleh karena itu,\Nkini keluarga kami berpisah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.38,0:11:49.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini soal perbedaan visi.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.46,0:11:52.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kayak band saja, dong!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:52.26,0:11:53.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keluarga macam itu ada, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.96,0:11:56.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku senang Ai pulang ke sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:56.98,0:12:00.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktu kecil, kau sering main\Ndengan anak-anak kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau lebih tua setahun dari Nagi, sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.14,0:12:04.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.04,0:12:06.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, di mana Nagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.98,0:12:08.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.66,0:12:16.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini enak!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:17.40,0:12:19.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perut itu memang harus diisi!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.72,0:12:20.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iya, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.12,0:12:24.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ongkos bus untuk berdua pun sudah...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.18,0:12:24.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sisanya bagianmu, Umino.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:26.74,0:12:27.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.78,0:12:29.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau boleh makan sisanya, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.38,0:12:32.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak perlu, kok.\NCukup kentang saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.90,0:12:34.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak bisa begitu!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.44,0:12:37.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita tidak tahu kapan lagi bisa makan.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.48,0:12:38.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi ini artinya
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.14,0:12:41.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,ciuman tidak langsung dengan Segawa!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.82,0:12:43.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kumakan!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.44,0:12:45.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuminum!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.82,0:12:48.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino, kau heboh sekali, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.74,0:12:50.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini perayaan soalnya!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.46,0:12:51.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perayaan?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak ada pilihan lain selain\Nbergantung ke Amano.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:57.00,0:12:57.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jujur saja, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:59.00,0:13:05.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku diam-diam berharap kalau\NAmano akan menolongku lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.68,0:13:09.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Segawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.32,0:13:13.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kau masih ingat yang terjadi waktu itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.58,0:13:16.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan ajak aku bicara lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.36,0:13:17.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:18.42,0:13:19.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku masih ingat.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.08,0:13:25.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau berubah waktu itu karena ulahku, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.32,0:13:28.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, Umino.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.92,0:13:32.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ingin tahu kenapa aku\Nterobsesi jadi peringkat satu?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.10,0:13:33.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.34,0:13:36.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin menyingkirkan tunanganku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menyingkirkan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.46,0:13:41.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sangat cinta dengan kuil keluargaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.62,0:13:45.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuil dengan 1.300 tahun sejarah,\Nmewarisinya tentu tak mudah.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.84,0:13:51.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejak aku kecil, aku diberi tahu\Nkalau aku sudah punya tunangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.26,0:13:53.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan aku tidak bisa terima itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:53.96,0:13:54.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku paham.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.66,0:14:00.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski tanpa bantuan tunanganku pun,\Naku bisa melindungi kuil sendirian.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:00.78,0:14:02.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itulah kenapa aku terus jadi yang terbaik
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.02,0:14:05.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan berusaha membuat orang tuaku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.60,0:14:07.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh keren.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.26,0:14:10.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tetapi,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:10.26,0:14:12.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino muncul di hadapanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.58,0:14:17.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada alasan lain kenapa\Naku jadi yang terbaik dalam belajar.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.52,0:14:20.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku punya tunangan,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku tak ingin seorang pun mendekatiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.84,0:14:27.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku malah mendekatimu walau aku tahu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.16,0:14:30.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habis, suatu saat\Nakan tiba waktunya berpisah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:31.56,0:14:33.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu akan sangat menyakitkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.68,0:14:38.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Segawa, ternyata kau itu\Ngampang kesepian juga, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:39.54,0:14:40.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa iya?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:41.06,0:14:42.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak juga, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.76,0:14:43.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Imut sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.66,0:14:48.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi alasan di balik\Nberubahnya Segawa waktu itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.26,0:14:52.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk mencegah\Norang seperti Umino mendekatiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.06,0:14:56.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sebabnya aku berpikir kalau terbaik
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.78,0:14:59.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,dalam satu hal saja tidak cukup.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.56,0:15:03.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus jadi yang terbaik dalam\Npenampilan, olahraga, dan komunikasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:03.50,0:15:06.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hingga aku sampai ke tempat\Ndi mana orang tak bisa menjangkau.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.06,0:15:10.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi begitu selama ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.60,0:15:13.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Segalanya hanya untuk menjauhiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi akibatnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.80,0:15:17.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,orang-orang malah mendekatiku,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.06,0:15:21.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,sampai aku sadar sekolah jadi\Nmenyenangkan karena itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.28,0:15:22.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlebih,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.38,0:15:26.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Aku pasti akan menang darimu!"
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.84,0:15:29.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Meski begitu Umino tetap mendekat.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.80,0:15:30.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terpikir, tidak?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.64,0:15:33.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Jangan ajak aku bicara lagi!"
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.48,0:15:40.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin sejak hari itulah\Ntakdirku mulai berubah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.00,0:15:42.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu artinya...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.98,0:15:48.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei! Dilarang nikmati masa muda!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:49.04,0:15:51.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saya adalah polisi masa muda!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:51.66,0:15:53.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Erika, kenapa di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.36,0:15:55.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau membaca pesanku?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:55.76,0:15:58.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian berdua, ikut aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.36,0:16:01.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tertukar saat lahir dan bertunangan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.62,0:16:04.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oleh karena itu,\Ndia sudah tidak tinggal di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:04.62,0:16:05.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.78,0:16:07.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengejutkan, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.46,0:16:10.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa coba yang bisa\Nmenduga hal seperti ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.48,0:16:13.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada yang tidak mungkin di dunia ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:13.78,0:16:15.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai berpikir begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.46,0:16:16.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.72,0:16:17.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada benarnya, sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.00,0:16:20.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tidak terkejut.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.82,0:16:32.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku adalah tunangan dari orang ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.90,0:16:33.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.58,0:16:38.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saya sungguh mohon maaf\Natas perbuatan tunangan saya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.24,0:16:45.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi itu orangnya selalu was-was,\Nmudah khawatir dan keras kepala.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.26,0:16:50.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi terkadang dia bertindak nekat\Nyang tidak ada gunanya seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:52.06,0:16:54.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia ini sungguh merepotkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.14,0:16:56.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino jadi ciut.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:57.18,0:17:00.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bertindak itu harus memikirkan\Nkeadaan orang lain juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:02.70,0:17:06.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku tidak menyangka kalau\Nkalian berdua bertunangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.32,0:17:10.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat Hiro membawa kalian kemari\Nkalian tidak terlihat seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.46,0:17:13.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habis, waktu itu aku juga\Ntidak tahu soal hubungan mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.60,0:17:20.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu benar, kami merahasiakan\Nsoal ini di sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.16,0:17:26.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terlebih, saya sendiri juga melawan\Nsaat dijodohkan oleh orang tua saya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.68,0:17:28.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.14,0:17:29.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Erika...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.72,0:17:34.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pada awalnya, saya bahkan sampai\Ntak mau bicara dengan Papa dan Nagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.54,0:17:38.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi akhirnya saya sadar kalau itu salah.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saya bukan sedang melawan,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.30,0:17:44.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi hanya melarikan diri.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:46.26,0:17:50.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, saya bahkan tak mencoba\Nmenghadapi masalah pertunangan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.34,0:17:55.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hiro adalah putri tunggal kesayangan kami,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.80,0:17:58.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi dia juga adalah pewaris kuil ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.68,0:18:02.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untuk membuatnya sadar akan itu,\Ntidak aneh kalau kami keras padanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.48,0:18:10.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, itu juga karena\Nkami ingin Hiro bahagia.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.62,0:18:15.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya kami juga harus\Nsaling bicara secara baik-baik lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.74,0:18:18.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ibu...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:20.42,0:18:23.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf atas masalah\Nyang telah terjadi kali ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:28.06,0:18:30.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sungguh berterima kasih hari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:30.86,0:18:34.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berkatmu, aku jadi sadar\Nkalau selama ini aku hanya lari.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.00,0:18:38.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak enak karena\Nsudah berlagak di depan ibumu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:38.60,0:18:40.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah kalau kau terbantu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.92,0:18:42.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beda sama si anu.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:44.06,0:18:45.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Erika!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.92,0:18:48.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku senang kau ada di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.80,0:18:53.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kapan-kapan kita belanja bareng lagi, yuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:55.16,0:18:55.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.08,0:18:57.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Canggung sekali rasanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.02,0:18:59.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Umino juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.62,0:19:02.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku cuma mengacau saja, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.36,0:19:03.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.84,0:19:11.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berisik sekali kau ini, ada apa, sih?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.40,0:19:13.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku konyol sekali, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:13.32,0:19:15.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal aku niatnya kabur bersama.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.40,0:19:19.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku malah ditolong oleh tunanganku\Ndan sampai dibuat minta maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.88,0:19:21.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu tidak benar, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:21.50,0:19:22.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.60,0:19:24.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi itu kuat, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:24.66,0:19:27.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau aku di posisimu\Naku pasti mati karena malu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.46,0:19:36.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih atas usahamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:39.94,0:19:42.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sup jagung di tengah musim panas?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.06,0:19:44.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi tidak buruk juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:46.00,0:19:48.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak ada yang kalahkan minuman soda dingin!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.22,0:19:51.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau beli soda untukmu sendiri?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.98,0:19:53.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tulisannya "membuat lega", sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:55.94,0:19:58.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini aku jadi tersadarkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:58.42,0:20:00.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Walau secara tak sadar,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.62,0:20:03.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,ketika aku ada masalah,\Naku bergantung pada Amano.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:04.54,0:20:08.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan kalau tak ada kau sekarang,\Nmungkin aku belum bisa bangkit.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.54,0:20:09.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, ya...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.08,0:20:11.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, begitulah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:12.54,0:20:15.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi tidak bisa apa-apa\Nkalau tidak ada aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.88,0:20:18.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan klaim sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.40,0:20:24.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau ingin ke rumah kakak?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.94,0:20:27.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cuma bertukar salam lalu pulang, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.66,0:20:28.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boleh, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.72,0:20:30.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan rumahku juga, sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.32,0:20:31.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.72,0:20:34.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga penasaran reaksinya kakak.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.84,0:20:35.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.26,0:20:39.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,tujuh tahun yang lalu,\Nkakak menyatakan perasaannya padamu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.34,0:20:46.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bolehkah aku beri jawaban\Nsaat kita berjumpa lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.66,0:20:53.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lucu, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:53.36,0:20:55.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak SD menyatakan perasaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.67,0:20:56.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:56.33,0:20:56.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.34,0:21:00.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada sesuatu yang ingin\Nkusampaikan mengenai hal itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.96,0:21:02.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia masih ingat...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.88,0:21:07.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Teman masa kecilnya Nagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.22,0:21:08.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:09.08,0:21:11.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bilang ingin ketemu kakak.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.22,0:21:12.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau punya orang seperti itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.06,0:21:15.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:15.76,0:21:16.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:16.82,0:21:17.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukan,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.84,0:21:18.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dik Nagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.14,0:21:21.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tumbuh seperti yang kubayangkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.02,0:21:23.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dik Nagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.16,0:21:24.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.74,0:21:26.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku datang untuk memberi jawaban.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:27.14,0:21:31.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dulu kau menembakku\Nketika aku pindah, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.80,0:21:33.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi itu kan dulu...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:34.29,0:21:35.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau nembak dia?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Kau tukang nembak orang!\N- Jangan memperkeruh suasana!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.34,0:21:39.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuberi tahu jawabanku.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:39.56,0:21:40.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak perlu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.66,0:21:42.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sudah lama, dilupakan saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.60,0:21:43.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.50,0:21:48.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku punya alasan tersendiri\Natas kepulanganku ke Jepang.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:50.24,0:21:54.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kali ini Ai pulang\Ndemi menikah dengan Nagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.98,0:21:55.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Eh?\N- Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:57.48,0:21:58.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menikah?!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.12,0:22:04.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ai lega bisa mengatakannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:35.94,0:23:38.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,100 kali lipat dari itu.
